---

---

<section
    class="med-section med-section-local"
>
    <div class="med-absolute med-inset-0 med-opacity-10 med-pointer-events-none">
        <svg class="med-w-full med-h-full">
            <pattern
                id="ropePattern"
                x="0"
                y="0"
                width="100"
                height="20"
                patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse"
            >
                <path d="M0 10 Q 25 0 50 10 T 100 10" fill="none" stroke="#34d399" stroke-width="2"
                ></path>
            </pattern>
            <rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="url(#ropePattern)"></rect>
        </svg>
    </div>

    <div class="med-container">
        <div class="med-grid">
            <div class="med-info-column">
                <span
                    class="med-tag med-tag-local"
                    >Velocidad Primitiva</span
                >
                <h2 class="med-title med-title-local">El Nudo</h2>

                <p class="med-description med-description-local">
                    ¿Cómo mides la velocidad en medio del océano si no tienes referencias? No hay
                    postes de kilómetros. El agua se mueve contigo.
                </p>

                <div
                    class="med-card med-card-local med-card--left-border"
                >
                    <h3 class="med-card-title med-card-title-local">La Corredera</h3>
                    <p class="med-card-text med-card-text-local">
                        Los marineros lanzaban un tronco al agua atado a una cuerda. La cuerda tenía
                        nudos cada 14.4 metros (47 pies y 3 pulgadas).
                    </p>
                    <p class="med-mt-4 med-text-sm med-leading-relaxed" style="color: #d1fae5;">
                        Mientras un marinero sostenía un reloj de arena de 30 segundos, otro contaba
                        cuántos nudos pasaban por sus manos.
                    </p>
                    <p class="med-card-note med-card-note-local">
                        7 nudos en 30 segundos = 7 millas náuticas por hora.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="med-visual-column med-visual-column-local">
                <div
                    class="med-relative med-w-full med-h-full med-flex med-items-center med-justify-center med-overflow-hidden med-rounded-lg med-border" style="background-color: #064e3b; border-color: #065f46;"
                >
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 400 200" class="med-w-full med-h-full">
                        <rect x="0" y="100" width="400" height="100" fill="#065f46" opacity="0.5"
                        ></rect>

                        <path d="M -50 100 L 450 100" stroke="#d1fae5" stroke-width="4"></path>

                        <g class="animate-rope-move">
                            {
                                Array.from({ length: 5 }).map((_, i) => (
                                    <g transform={`translate(${i * 100}, 100)`}>
                                        <circle cx="0" cy="0" r="6" fill="#10b981" />
                                        <text
                                            x="0"
                                            y="-15"
                                            text-anchor="middle"
                                            fill="#6ee7b7"
                                            font-size="10"
                                        >
                                            KNOT
                                        </text>
                                    </g>
                                ))
                            }
                        </g>

                        <path d="M 190 130 L 200 105 L 210 130" fill="#ecfdf5"></path>
                        <text x="200" y="150" text-anchor="middle" fill="#ecfdf5" font-size="12"
                            >MARK</text
                        >
                    </svg>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .med-section-local {
        background-color: #022c22;
        color: #d1fae5;
    }

    .med-tag-local {
        color: #34d399;
        border-color: #065f46;
    }

    .med-title-local {
        color: #ecfdf5;
    }

    .med-description-local {
        color: #d1fae5;
        opacity: 0.9;
    }

    .med-card-title-local {
        color: #6ee7b7;
    }

    .med-card-text-local {
        color: #d1fae5;
    }

    .med-card-note-local {
        color: #34d399;
    }

    .med-visual-column-local {
        height: 300px;
    }

    .med-card-local {
        background-color: color-mix(in srgb, #064e3b 50%, transparent);
        border-color: #10b981;
    }

    @keyframes ropeMove {
        0% {
            transform: translateX(0);
        }
        100% {
            transform: translateX(-100px);
        }
    }
    .animate-rope-move {
        animation: ropeMove 1s linear infinite;
    }
</style>
